  > The binary accepts three flags (from `CliArgs::parse()`):
  > 
  > | Flag | Aliases | Argument | Description |
  > |------|---------|----------|-------------|
  > | `-h` | `--help` | none | Print usage help and exit |
  > | `-f` | `--folder` | `&lt;PATH&gt;` | Open this folder on launch |
  > | `-t` | `--thumbnail-size`, `--thumb-size` | `&lt;SIZE&gt;` | Thumbnail tile size: a number (e.g. 160) or WxH format (e.g. 120x160). Tiles are square, so the larger dimension is used. |
  > 
  > Settings passed via CLI override persisted settings and are remembered afterward.
