  > ## 2. KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS / HOTKEYS
  > 
  > ### Rebindable Actions (Customizable in Preferences → Hotkeys)
  > 
  > Source: `/home/grymmjack/git/pixel-viewer/src/app.rs:512-540` (enum Action)
  > 
  > | Default Key | Action | Context |
  > |-------------|--------|---------|
  > | **← (Left Arrow)** | Previous image | Single view (viewer mode) |
  > | **→ (Right Arrow)** | Next image | Single view (viewer mode) |
  > | **Esc (Escape)** | Back to grid | Single view — return to grid view |
  > | **Backspace** | Parent directory | Navigate to parent folder |
  > 
  > Users can rebind these four actions via **Preferences → Hotkeys → Rebind**.
  > 
  > ### Fixed Keyboard Shortcuts (Non-rebindable)
  > 
  > Source: `/home/grymmjack/git/pixel-viewer/src/app.rs:8458-8485` (HOTKEYS constant) plus code at lines 5911, 5952, 6163, 6171, 6219-6230, 6236, 6051-6091, 6134-6139
  > 
  > | Key Combination | Action | Mode | Notes |
  > |-----------------|--------|------|-------|
  > | **Ctrl + / / Ctrl -** | Zoom whole UI | All | Adjust egui zoom factor for entire interface |
  > | **Ctrl + Wheel / Pinch** | Resize thumbnails (grid) or zoom image (viewer) | All | Grid: changes thumbnail size; Viewer: zooms the displayed image |
  > | **Wheel** | Previous / next image (viewer) or scroll (grid) | All | Viewer: if image fits the window, wheel advances images; if image overflows, wheel scrolls. Grid: scrolls the thumbnail grid |
  > | **Mouse Back / Fwd button** | Folder history (grid) or prev/next image (viewer) | All | Grid: navigate folder history; Viewer: step through images |
  > | **Home / End** | Select first / last item | Grid | Jumps and scrolls to first or last file in grid |
  > | **/** (Slash) | Filter thumbnails by filename | Grid | Opens the "/" filter bar for quick filename search |
  > | **F11** | Immersive / fullscreen mode | Single view | Hides all UI bars/panels, shows only the image; cursor auto-hides after 1.5s of stillness; mouse at screen edges reveals controls |
  > | **R** | Load random 16colo.rs pack | Any | Launches async fetch of a random scene art pack; suppressed while typing/searching |
  > | **Ctrl + F** | Open advanced recursive search | Grid | Opens the "Find images..." dialog for searching by name, type, dimensions, SAUCE metadata |
  > | **Esc** | Close search/filter dialogs | Grid | Closes advanced search window or "/" filename filter |
  > | **F** | Toggle fit-to-window mode (viewer) | Single view | Toggles sticky fit; when enabled, new images auto-fit to window. Also shows in HOTKEYS as "Fit to window + auto-fit new images (viewer)" |
  > | **T** | Toggle tile preview mode (viewer) | Single view | Tiles the image across the entire window for texture/pattern testing |
  > | **1–5** | Set star rating (1 to 5 stars) | Single view | Rate the current image; suppressed while typing/renaming |
  > | **0** | Clear star rating | Single view | Removes the rating (sets to 0); suppressed while typing |
  > | **Z (held) + 1–9** | Set zoom to 100–900% | Single view | Hold Z, then press a digit 1–9 to jump to that zoom level. Text-mode/pixel-perfect art shows in whole device pixels per source pixel (e.g., Z+3 = 3×) |
  > | **Z (held) + 0** | Set zoom to 1000% (10×) | Single view | Hold Z, then press 0 to zoom to 1000% |
  > | **Z (held) + Plus / Equals** | Step zoom up one level | Single view | Hold Z and press `+` or `=` to increment zoom using the pixel-perfect ladder |
  > | **Z (held) + Minus** | Step zoom down one level | Single view | Hold Z and press `-` to decrement zoom |
  > | **Ctrl + C** | Copy selection | Grid | Copies selected files to clipboard |
  > | **Ctrl + X** | Cut selection | Grid | Cuts selected files for moving |
  > | **Ctrl + V** | Paste | Grid | Pastes copied/cut files |
  > | **Ctrl + N** | New folder | Grid | Creates a new folder in the current directory |
  > | **F2** | Rename | Grid | Enters rename mode for the selected file/folder |
  > | **Delete** | Move to trash | Grid | Deletes the selected file(s) to trash |
  > | **Ctrl + Z** | Undo last file operation | Grid | Undoes the most recent copy/cut/move operation |
  > | **Click** | Open image / enter folder | Grid | Left-click a tile to open an image or descend into a folder |
  > | **Ctrl + Click** | Toggle selection | Grid | Hold Ctrl and click to add/remove from current selection |
  > | **Shift + Click** | Range-select | Grid | Hold Shift and click to select all items between the anchor and clicked item |
  > | **Right-click** | File operations context menu | Grid | Opens menu with copy/cut/paste/rename/delete/new folder options |
  > | **Drag** | Pan the image | Single view | Click and drag the image to pan; or click/drag the minimap (navigator) on the right edge to jump to that view |
